        <p><span class="pick-ltrs">I</span>nterest - Does it interest me?</p>
        <p><span class="pick-ltrs">C</span>omprehend - Do I understand it?</p>
        <p><span class="pick-ltrs">K</span>now - I know most of the words</p>

        <h4 class="text-center">The 5 "Finger Tips" of Choosing a Book to Read</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Open your book to any page.</li>
            <li>Read the words on that page.</li>
            <li>Count then number of words you do not know on that page.</li>
            <li>Now use the "finger tips" to help you decide if this is a good book for you to read by yourself.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p><%= image_tag 'finger1.png', class:'img-fluid fingers' %>  One word = OK</p>
        
        <p><%= image_tag 'finger2.png', class:'img-fluid fingers' %>  Two words = Still a good choice</p>
        <p><%= image_tag 'finger3.png', class:'img-fluid fingers' %>  Three words = You may need help reading this</p>
        <p><%= image_tag 'finger4.png', class:'img-fluid fingers' %>  Four words = Tough to read</p>
        <p><%= image_tag 'finger5.png', class:'img-fluid fingers' %>  Five words = Try a different book</p>
